---
title: Easy Peri Peri Chicken & Slaw Bowl with Garlic-Corn Rice & Garlic Aioli
description: A peri peri sauce is double trouble in the best way when it combines with our favourite Aussie spice blend on tender chicken. Pile everything on top of a fragrant rice tossed with charred corn for a dinner that will sure to make you smile. It’s fun times ahead, tonight!

